<h1>Hello, <%= @ta['name'] %>!</h1>

<hr />

<div>
  Thanks for signing up to volunteer as a TA with Girl Develop It Chicago! Your application has been received and will be reviewed by your chapter leaders.
</div>

<div>
  Once your application is processed, you will receive a confirmation email with instructions on signing up to volunteer for classes.
</div>

<div>
  -- <br />
  Cheers, <br />
  <%= CHAPTER_NAME %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= image_tag attachments['logo.png'].url, alt: 'Girl Develop It', size: '100x100' %>
</div>

<div id="footer">
  <div class="small">
    <em>This email was sent because you signed up with <a href="http://<%= BASE_URL %>"><%= CHAPTER_NAME %></a> as a volunteer TA.</em>
  </div>
</div>
